            <title><![CDATA[【[生病]“嗓子疼”不一定是新冠！摸清病因客观对待】上呼吸道和咽喉是人体的门户，不论是流感病毒还是新冠病毒，或是细菌感染，都可能导致咽喉肿痛。应注意鉴别...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[生病]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shengbing-b740fa9852.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>“嗓子疼”不一定是新冠！摸清病因客观对待】上呼吸道和咽喉是人体的门户，不论是流感病毒还是新冠病毒，或是细菌感染，都可能导致咽喉肿痛。应注意鉴别，区别对待，对症规范治疗。同时，坚持保持手卫生、勤通风等良好个人卫生习惯，有助于减少传播风险、防治各类传染病。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%96%AB%E7%82%B9%E9%80%9A%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%96%AB%E7%82%B9%E9%80%9A%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫疫点通#</span></a>  <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4903101824696407" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">健康中国的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0035PbOdly1he3ml1acc9j60zk0k076c02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Sctv47Fglx085yGNSdkI01041200fFMb0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684729809&amp;ssig=FPU8pQr66K&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/By7pOohWlx085yGNkX9m010412007xNp0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684729809&amp;ssig=fFm1deKmRE&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/wZVCcUsElx085yGNjTQY010412004Jmt0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684729809&amp;ssig=YX0UKNbdTt&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4903101824696407&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
