        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[冲刺]深圳发布第二套校园脊柱健康操！挺直腰板，一起学起！】为了缓解中小学生因长期不良姿势而引发的局部肌肉紧张、改善姿态异常、减少中小学生脊柱侧弯重症...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[冲刺]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/ac/2022_Sprint_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>深圳发布第二套校园脊柱健康操！挺直腰板，一起学起！】为了缓解中小学生因长期不良姿势而引发的局部肌肉紧张、改善姿态异常、减少中小学生脊柱侧弯重症发生率，深圳市青少年脊柱健康中心联合相关体育机构，共同研发第二套校园脊柱健康操。该脊柱健康操结合了体育锻炼和医学理论，涵括了脊柱各部位的伸展、旋转、屈曲等动作，旨在促进血液循环，增强脊柱肌群的力量和柔韧性，同时改善中小学生的异常体态！快和娃一起学起来👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23521%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E6%97%A5%23&amp;extparam=%23521%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E6%97%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#521世界脊柱健康日#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E9%9D%92%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E4%BE%A7%E5%BC%AF%E9%98%B2%E6%B2%BB%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E9%9D%92%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E4%BE%A7%E5%BC%AF%E9%98%B2%E6%B2%BB%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳发布青少年脊柱侧弯防治标准#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4903929478054013" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1he69lykl5ij21hc0u0tdv.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/DsgF2qt7gx085Cqy8WMw01041201f69t0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BThihd3VLAY5R&amp;Expires=1684729772&amp;ssig=t4xNfqPPT6&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/D4ZVnpeRgx085CqxEVQc01041200EnIe0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BThihd3VLAY5R&amp;Expires=1684729772&amp;ssig=ACEjP2loF0&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/jrlda6iVgx085CqvYJGM01041200pBz20E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BThihd3VLAY5R&amp;Expires=1684729772&amp;ssig=IZGidD6Pgw&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4903929478054013&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
